h3.title: Arbor Day Celebration and Tree Planting

a.h3: Arbor Day Celebration and Tree Planting
a.div: The Village of Fox Point hosted it’s 49th Arbor Day Celebration at Maple Dale School today (Friday, April 26 at 3:00 p.m). The public celebration included our students, community, and village officials who were present for a tree planting along with the dedication and presentation of this year’s Tree City Flag by the WI Department of Natural Resources.
